{"tid":1786200,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要說「藍色經濟不道德」，試着說「我覺得藍色經濟好嘔心，好污糟，好核突」","createTime":"2019-12-17T03:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T12:05:14.000Z","uid":131691,"like":135,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5a21521d89828f642c5e27c942289db852014c","tid":1786200,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:27:37.000Z","msg":"歷史上，成功嘅羣衆式經濟制裁，都唔係用道德理性做招徠<br />\n個出發點開係道德理性，但係個成功之處係將道德理性化爲羣衆情緒，感性地厭惡敵方嘅一切<br />\n因爲咁樣先可以由小雨點變爲瀑布<br />\n<br />\n所以與其說「藍色經濟不道德」或「撐警不道德」<br />\n不如說：<br />\n「嗰間藍店，聽到個名都想作嘔」<br />\n「佢個老闆撐警，我覺得好核突囉，行過都聞到口臭」<br />\n「嗰套戲個演員舐共，上映嗰時成個戲院都有浸臭味」<br />\n「嗰間餐廳係藍店嚟，真係唔知食咗會唔會肚屙」<br />\n「嗰個同事撐警，公司office近佢嗰個角落行過都會覺得唔舒服」<br />\n等等，總之：<br />\n藍=病<br />\n藍=有問題<br />\n藍=不正常<br />\n藍=要消除"},{"pid":"78e01ca0dce83c5622a3b2c0dd8c307dd2469d76","tid":1786200,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:28:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"031a07953485d8a0ad50acd13ecbe4b121eb229f","tid":1786200,"uid":198843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"76e8f4be2662ab46f902a5861dc71da56e6d1e01","tid":1786200,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97be344a5fc6562e3ce6817ceac4c0555c9bc1c0","tid":1786200,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c486d042b09d2bff5ada24fcd91e90adee84cf","tid":1786200,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef50f0f93ddde69ad466f04af2d5bbda0433de6b","tid":1786200,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.g